descriptions.see_description: In the input, you should see...either a long or tall black grid with 2 different colored pixels
descriptions.grid_description: The output grid size... remains the same.
descriptions.do_description: To make the output, you have to... create a pattern of short stripes alternating between the 2 colors. Start from the first colored pixel and create a line that goes to the opposite side using that color. Then go to the second colored pixel and do the same. Continue the pattern of stripes to the RIGHT for a long grid or go DOWN for a tall grid all the way to the end.
